name: Octobservant
text:
Whenever Octobservant deals combat damage to a player, draw a card.
Flood {2}{u}{u} (During your turn, you may pay {2}{u}{u} and exile this card from your hand flooding target land an opponent controls. It loses all land types and abilities, and it gains “{T}: Add {1}.”) 
Whenever flooded land becomes tapped, you draw a card.
